        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–7. Holotypes of Fingulus spp. and their labels. 1, F. brevirostris Ren, 1983, dorsal view; 2, same, lateral view; 3, same, ventral view; 4, same, head, dorsal view; 5, same, labels; 6, F. ruficeps Hsiao & Ren, 1983, head, dorsal view; 7, same, labels. Scales in mm. © NKUM." ;
