        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 20–23. Holotype of Fingulus umbonatus Stonedahl & Cassis, 1991. 20, dorsal view; 21, lateral view (arrow shows strongly prominent tubercle of prosternal xiphus); 22, frontal view; 23, labels. Scale in mm; labels not to scale. © BPBM, courtesy of D.A. Polhemus." ;
